<SLUG> BC-BOOK-SPOCK-TEX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
PEDIATRICIAN TO A NATION: A PERSONAL LOOK AT THE MAN WHO CHANGED
PARENTING
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By CAROLYN POIROT 
c.1998 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
