   &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (Adds: US-CHINA; CLINTON-INVESTIGATION; CONGRESS-GAYS;
CONGRESS-SUICIDE; BIOLOGICAL-THREAT; JASPER-ATTORNEYS;
APARTMENTS-HOUSTON; GLF-BAKER-FINCH; and BBN-ASTROS.)
</P>
<P>
   &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (The ``HNS'' tag appears in all sluglines.)
