   NEW MEXICO -- RICHARDSON. Senate Energy and Natural Resources
Committee Chairman Frank Murkowski is expected to meet with Bill
Richardson this week. Interview with Murkowksi on when hearings can
be expected and what he plans to talk to Richardson about.
(Possible.) Gorman
</P>
