seat in the U.S. Senate is meeting with reporters in Washington
Tuesday. Eckstein
</P>
<P>
   -- PROCTER&AMP;GAMBLE-NEY. Follow-up on story on Rep. Bob Ney's
dispute with Procter &AMP; Gamble lobbyist over campaign donations and
votes on trade issues. Egbert
</P>
