the need to speed up aid to farmers and ranchers reeling from this
spring's drought. (Contingent on vote.) Brown
</P>
<P>
   VIRGIN ISLANDS -- PR. The future status of Puerto Rico was the
subject of a Senate committee hearing Tuesday. Feldman
