<DOCNO> NYT19980714.0362 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-14 21:17 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4941 &Cx1f; tic-z
